  "title": "Rich Silky Malaysian Olive Curry",
  "description": "A malty and silky Malaysian dish featuring olives, perfect for a monsoon evening, this paleo-friendly curry is a hearty and flavorful option. It is made with a variety of spices and simmered to perfection.",
