  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large pan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onions and cook until they are translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for another minute.",
    "Add the curry powder, cumin powder, and coriander powder and cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Pour in the canned coconut milk and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "Add the green olives and cook for 10 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Season the curry with sea salt to taste.",
    "Serve the curry hot over rice or with some naan bread."
